Package com.googlecode.cqengine.persistence.support

Interface Summary
ObjectStore<O> An interface providing similar methods as Set, except the methods accept QueryOptions.
 

Class Summary
CollectionWrappingObjectStore<O> An ObjectStore which wraps a Collection and delegates all method calls to the collection.
ConcurrentOnHeapObjectStore<O> An ObjectStore which wraps a concurrent implementation of Set.
FilteredObjectStore<O> Wraps an ObjectStore and filters objects returned by its iterator to ensure they match a given query.
ObjectSet<O> Represents a set of objects which may be iterated repeatedly, allowing the resources opened for each iteration to be closed afterwards.
ObjectStoreAsSet<O> Adapts an ObjectStore to behave like a Set, using an existing connection to the persistence when methods belonging to the Set interface are called.
ObjectStoreResultSet<O> Created by npgall on 01/03/2016.
PersistenceFlags Constants for flags which may be set into query options by the query engine internally.
